<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="un6023bn"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="un6" href="#un6023">UN6: </a>  <a href="../../ff/unbs/un6all.htm#un6023bn"> (NLI.4) 23(bn)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Gov. lives in the Convent,</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The <mark>residence of the governor, still denominated the convent</mark>, was, in ancient times, a most extensive convent of Franciscan friars; the peculiar arms of which, although plastered over, are still embedded in the wall of the north corridor. As a dwelling, it is well situation, spacious, and tolerably commodious. It commands a fine view of the bay, has an extensive garden, and accommodations suited to the high rank of its occupant. <small> An Old Inhabitant, <a name="TTHG1" href="/udra/udex.htm#tthg1"><cite title="source">The traveller's handbook for Gibraltar</cite></a> (1844), 27</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c07250f" href="../../../f/ff/fnbs/c07all.htm#c07250f">VI.C.07:250(f)</a> </dd> </dd></dl>
